(Andres Freund)
     </para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Andrew Dunstan <andrew@dunslane.net>
Branch: master [3b174b1a3] 2019-01-10 15:53:45 -0500
Branch: REL_11_STABLE [076ffbcb5] 2019-01-10 16:24:57 -0500
